  m_TableData:
  - m_Id: 5298429952
    m_Localized: Back
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 187096342528
    m_Localized: 'Basic Controls


      - WASD To Move


      - E to Switch Weapons


      -
      R to Reload


      - F to Pickup Item / Interact


      - LMB to shoot (when
      not commanding operators)'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 884755898368
    m_Localized: 'Command / Interaction Control


      Right Click an Operator to
      select them.


      Right Click a target area or item to Command them

      -
      When commanded to go to an empty area, the Operator will go to the area and
      hold the position until commanded otherwise

      - When commanded to go to
      an item, the Operator will go to the area nad pickup the item

      - When
      commanded to go to the player, the Operator will follow the player until commanded
      otherwise


      Hold right Click to to command all operators to follow you


      While
      commanding an Operator, you can Hold Right Click to exit command mode'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1153308794880
    m_Localized: CAPTURE ALL THE WHITE ZONES TO WIN
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
